12
00:01:02.537 --> 00:01:07.992
♪ 'Cause all I need is you ♪

13
00:01:08.549 --> 00:01:14.410
♪ If I had the world today ♪

14
00:01:19.111 --> 00:01:23.823
♪ I would throw it all away ♪

15
00:01:23.863 --> 00:01:27.978
♪ Ay ♪

16
00:01:28.525 --> 00:01:34.525
♪ 'Cause all I need is you ♪

17
00:01:39.479 --> 00:01:43.614
♪ All I need ♪

18
00:01:45.218 --> 00:01:46.784
♪

19
00:01:47.197 --> 00:01:50.805
♪ Is this as good as it's gonna get? ♪

20
00:01:50.849 --> 00:01:52.959
♪ I've given all I can give ♪

21
00:01:53.025 --> 00:01:57.003
